highlights.text: “Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 297 weeks straight.
“How Do I Say Goodbye” by Dean Lewis is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 51 spots at #131.
Bad Bunny has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Me Porto Bonito” is the highest at #6.
“THE LONELIEST” by Måneskin is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #71.
